  "blocks": [
    {
      "h2": "Unwind before you fly",
      "h3s": [],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Whether you are in the mood for a massage or a last-minute manicure, there is something for everyone. Browse through airport lounges, spas, relaxation areas and more.",
        "Showing 1-12 of 38 results",
        "Guests can enjoy comfortable seating, complimentary food and beverages, and thoughtfully designed areas for dining, working, or unwinding. Whether you're preparing for a long-haul journey or simply taking a moment to relax, the Aer Lingus Lounge offers a peaceful pre-departure experience inspired by the spirit of Ireland.",
        "A quiet escape for eligible passengers. Enjoy a buffet featuring authentic Indian cuisine, a self-service bar, and a comfortable atmosphere to relax before your flight.",
        "Relax at the recently renovated AirFrance Lounge while enjoying a view of the New York City skyline.",
        "American Airlines Admirals Club offers food, drinks, Wi-Fi, and a kids room.",
        "The American Express Centurion Lounge offers a premium experience for Platinum, Delta SkyMiles Reserve, and Centurion Card members. Featuring chef-curated dining, a full-service coffee bar, and a hidden speakeasy, it is the ideal destination to unwind before your flight.",
        "Be Relax has all you need for you to relax before the journey - from massaging chairs to nail services.",
        "JetBlue's new take on the airport lounge welcomes eligible travelers with 2 levels of thoughtfully designed spaces to play, work and lounge pre-flight. Features 2 bars, fresh food, and a relaxed vibe with nods to its NYC home. Complimentary access to TrueBlue Mosaic 4 members, JetBlue Premier Cardmembers, and JetBlue transatlantic customers traveling in Mint. (Lounge access not available with Blue Basic fares.)",
        "Offering dining stations, a full bar, a coffee bar, and private shower suites.",
        "A unique collaboration between Chase and Etihad Airways. Guests enjoy made-to-order dining, signature cocktails, and premium wellness amenities, including shower suites and prayer rooms in an intimate, upscale setting.",
        "Terminal 8's most exclusive lounge allows you to relax in an elegant, modern atmosphere. Sip a drink at the circular champagne bar or enjoy a meal prepared with our partners at the James Beard Foundation.",
        "Religious space for worship and prayer.",
        "The Delta One Lounge is Delta Air Lines' flagship retreat, reserved exclusively for Delta One travelers. With features including a relaxing spa, a full-service brasserie, and extensive luxury amenities, the lounge provides top-tier service and a refined pre-flight experience."
      ],
